name: cred-rea-fish-team-stationary-point-count-surveys-at-pearl-and-hermes-reef-2003
notes: Stationary Point Counts at 4 stations at each survey site were surveyed as part of Rapid Ecological Assessments conducted at 9 sites at Pearl and Hermes Reef in July and August, 2003 from the NOAA vessel Oscar Elton Sette (OES03-06). Raw survey data included species level abundance estimates.
